              "explanation": "The submission is logically consistent and meets the rubric. It explicitly analyzes the diphoton invariant mass (m_yy), performs a Gaussian-plus-quadratic fit over 100\u2013160 GeV, and reports a localized excess. The fitted mean is 123.97 GeV with \u03c3 \u2248 1.0 GeV, i.e., near 125 GeV. Residuals show clear positive deviations in the 123\u2013125 GeV bins, supporting the stated Higgs\u2011like excess around 125 GeV. The workflow, selections, uncertainties (sqrt(N)), and artifacts (spectrum, fit summary, residuals) are coherent and mutually consistent with the interpretation.",
